The paper deals with natural language processing tasks, specifically natural language inference, and introduces attentional mechanism in neural networks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper explores the use of syntax-based attention, which involves exploiting the underlying syntax of a sentence, and this could fall under the sub-category of Machine Learning (cs.LG) or Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also performs qualitative analysis, which could indicate that it belongs to the sub-category of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) or Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV).
